{"tid":2394057,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"足總前主席5,060萬沽美國銀行中心","createTime":"2021-02-04T02:24:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T02:44:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9819ef47f8467d7eaec02bd9858a77ae10deb2b9","tid":2394057,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T02:24:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210204/SRRABHQOVJGFJFXQPM4N42VSVU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210204%2FSRRABHQOVJGFJFXQPM4N42VSVU%2F&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRBx0icFY2nnrImD0qQ%2FuO9w%3D&h=67621318\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210204%2FSRRABHQOVJGFJFXQPM4N42VSVU%2F&h=98a6ec09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210204/SRRABHQOVJGFJFXQPM4N42VSVU/</a><br />\n<br />\n足總前主席5,060萬沽美國銀行中心<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FvoXUeG5q40MsdfHu1ICfsi1ZqI=/856x560/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7CC3VOE56JECZOGCLC6H2WUVVM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFvoXUeG5q40MsdfHu1ICfsi1ZqI%3D%2F856x560%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7CC3VOE56JECZOGCLC6H2WUVVM.jpg&h=1ba6f96e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■足總前主席梁孔德以5,060萬元沽出中環美國銀行中心一單位。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】工商舖自去年底撤銷雙辣稅，刺激相關物業交投轉活，美聯工商舖最新數據指，上月相關物業整體註冊量錄581宗，按月增加18.3%，連升五個月，並創自2019年6月爆發社會運動以來新高。不少投資者亦趁市況轉好沽貨，其中足球總會前主席梁孔德最新以5,060萬元，沽出中環美國銀行中心一單位。<br />\n<br />\n據土地註冊處資料，美國銀行中心19樓15室，面積約1,375方呎，新近以5,060萬元易手，呎價約3.68萬元。原業主為金喜有限公司，登記董事包括足總前主席梁孔德及其兒子梁麒繕。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，梁氏早於2011年共斥6,556.9萬元，購入該廈19樓3個單位，而早於2013年則以4,560萬元沽出其中兩個單位，連同最新售出最後1伙，梁氏多年來賬面獲利3,063.1萬元或約46.7%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去年與妻逾兩億買豪宅<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"1066f3fdba1c6608a373622439d15fcba073673b","tid":2394057,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T03:01:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b9e87be9b85fb3a190ebca80832dc7570920209","tid":2394057,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T01:17:26.000Z","msg":"走資<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5940316924e2d49ac67dd6ec26b4d93610b33194","tid":2394057,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T01:27:31.000Z","msg":"標題黨，以為沽成座中心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c34a8531951860da3704fb63c22b887e2e321714","tid":2394057,"uid":281483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T01:30:13.000Z","msg":"別讓領導走<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06d7f03b93d1c1e868387ff01d2148dc1c238470","tid":2394057,"uid":124655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5940316924e2d49ac67dd6ec26b4d93610b33194","tid":2394057,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T01:27:31.000Z","msg":"標題黨，以為沽成座中心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T01:37:20.000Z","msg":"香港人 買樓 = 買一個單位"},{"pid":"345a3d1c4f95a9a618cd8e88d52baa0c77077ada","tid":2394057,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T02:01:03.000Z","msg":"而家先走資？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6f8df93d8bc2f00b5c87a0bbc6e4b11460acff","tid":2394057,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc